The paper addresses the problem of evaluating learning systems in safety-critical domains, which is a common concern in the fields of artificial intelligence (AI), machine learning (ML), and robotics (RO). Therefore, cs.AI, cs.LG, and cs.RO are likely sub-categories. The paper also focuses on simulated driving, which is a common application of computer vision (CV) and control systems (SY). Therefore, cs.CV and cs.SY are also likely sub-categories.
